### the packages were located 

### checking the status of the mysql server
```
sudo systemctl status mysql
```

### the commend showed that mysql server was active and running

### trying to the mysql -u root commend agian

```
mysql -u root -p
```

### the result was an error message
ERROR 1698 (28000): Access denied for user 'root'@'localhost'

